jp.go.aist.six.oval.model.unix

Enum WaitStatusEnumeration

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<WaitStatusEnumeration>
      • jp.go.aist.six.oval.model.unix.WaitStatusEnumeration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<WaitStatusEnumeration>, OvalEnumeration, OvalObject

    public enum WaitStatusEnumeration
extends Enum<WaitStatusEnumeration>
implements OvalEnumeration
    The set of status types that specify whether the server that is invoked by inetd will take over the listening socket associated with the service, and whether once launched, inetd will wait for that server to exit, if ever, before it resumes listening for new service requests.
